![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1602102827550-NPW9IDQUEPORZI374Q8F/image-asset.jpeg)

The Mighty Morphin' Power Rangers were a pop culture phenomenon for anyone born in the 90's. With their fighting skills, cool gadgets and dino-themed robots, there was almost no team cooler. But what happens when these "Teenagers with Attitude" collide with the world's most FAMOUS superhero team, the Justice League? Watch fandoms collide as the likes of Batman, Wonder Woman, and Superman meet the Power Rangers for the first time, and brace yourself as forces of evil join together to rid the earth of these heroes once and for all. All that and LOAD of Power Rangers talk in this Morphenomenal episode of the Major Issues Podcast!  
